text: Pogonocherus penicillatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by John Eatton Le Conte in Agassizz in 1850. It is known from Canada and the United States.BioLib.cz - Pogonocherus penicillatus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1850
